sequenceDiagram
autonumber
participant Game
participant UI
participant Scoreboard
participant TurnManager

Game-->>Game: enter LevelComplete (freeze board)
Game->>UI: showWinMessage()

UI->>Scoreboard: addScore(amount)
Scoreboard-->>UI: updated

UI-->>Game: wait for choice
alt Next Level
  UI->>TurnManager: advanceLevel()
  TurnManager-->>Game: levelIndex++
  Game-->>Game: loadNextLevel()
else Restart
  UI->>Game: restartLevel()
  Game-->>Game: resetLevel()
else Exit
  UI->>Game: exitToMenu()
  Game-->>Game: mainMenu()
end